OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a cloudier day,
OL,6,Fperhaps with the odd shower, but it
OL,7,Fshould brighten up later in the day
OL,8,Fwith some warm sunshine, at least in
OL,9,Fthe west.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FSome late sunshine for most
OL,12,Fthen a dry night with some clear
OL,13,Fspells. Some fog patches in low lying
OL,14,Fareas arounddawn.
OL,15,
OL,16,CTuesday:FA dry day with some good
OL,17,Fsunny spells in the morning before
OL,18,Fcloud builds up for a time. Very warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
