OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FA dry
OL,6,Fand very warm few days with some sunny
OL,7,Fspells, and perhaps very hot on
OL,8,FThursday. Perhaps some thundery
OL,9,Fshowers later on Thursday and on Friday
